Hence $H_2(x) = 2 x H_1(x) - H_0(x) = 4x^2-2$, which satisfies
$$
\|H_2\|^2 = 16 âˆ«_{-âˆ}^âˆ x^4 w(x) {\rm d } x - 16âˆ«_{-âˆ}^âˆ x^2 w(x) {\rm d}x + 4 âˆ«_{-âˆ}^âˆ  w(x) {\rm d}x = 
